OL,3,CWelsh Secretary calls for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into preventable deaths in
OL,5,Cnorth Wales
OL,7,FThe Secretary of State for Wales,
OL,8,FDavid TC Davies MP, has called for a
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry into preventable deaths
OL,10,Fin north Wales.
OL,12,FIn a letter to Welsh Government health
OL,13,Fsecretary Elenud Morgan, seen by ITV
OL,14,FWales, Mr Davies said: "Too many
OL,15,Ffamilies in north Wales are being
OL,16,Fneedlessly bereaved."
