OL,5,Cnorth Wales
OL,7,FIt comes after an ITV Cymru Wales
OL,8,Finvestigation found Betsi Cadwaldr
OL,9,FUniversity Health Board had been
OL,10,Fhanded 28 "prevention of future deaths
OL,11,Freports" (PFD) over a 16-month period
OL,12,Fup to April 2024, more than the
OL,13,Fcombined number handed to the other
OL,14,Fsix Welsh health boards.
