OL,7,FIn response to our findings, Ms Morgan
OL,8,Fpreviously told us: "If there was good
OL,9,Freason to (have a public inquiry), of
OL,10,Fcourse I would consider that but at
OL,11,Fthe moment I don't think it's reached
OL,12,Fthat threshold."
OL,14,FA section of Mr Davies' letter said:
OL,15,F"I note that previously you have not
OL,16,Fsupported calls for a public inquiry
OL,17,Fon the number of preventable deaths in
OL,18,Fnorth Wales, citing the number of
OL,19,Fpreventable death notices in north
OL,20,FWales having not reached that
OL,21,Fthreshold.
