OL,3,CWelsh Secretary calls for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into preventable deaths in
OL,5,Cnorth Wales
OL,7,F"I disagree. Too many families in
OL,8,Fnorth Wales are being needlessly
OL,9,Fbereaved; their loved ones would still
OL,10,Fbe alive were it not for the board's
OL,11,Ffailings.
OL,13,F"I do not know what threshold you have
OL,14,Fin mind for calling a public inquiry.
OL,15,FBut I believeJthat by any impartial
OL,16,Fjudgment the case for a public inquiry
OL,17,Fhas long been met.
