OL,3,CWelsh Secretary calls for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into preventable deaths in
OL,5,Cnorth Wales
OL,7,F"I urge you to take decisive action
OL,8,Fand announce immediately a public
OL,9,Finquiry into preventable deaths in
OL,10,Fnorth Wales. I stand ready to do all
OL,11,Fthat I can to support such an inquiry."
OL,13,FA Welsh Government spokesperson
OL,14,Fconfirmed they have received the
OL,15,Fletter and will response in due course.
OL,17,FSince our initial report, ITV Wales
OL,18,Fhas been contacted by families whose
OL,19,Floved ones' deaths were also the
OL,20,Fsubject of prevention of future death
OL,21,Fnotices.
