OL,7,FIn a statement, Ms Shillabeer said:
OL,8,F"We are reaching out to families of
OL,9,Floved ones who have had a prevention
OL,10,Fof future death notice issued
OL,11,Ffollowing the inquest into their death
OL,12,Fover the last year in particular.
OL,14,F"We want to apologise and offer them
OL,15,Fthe opportunity to meet with us to
OL,16,Fdiscuss their experience. This will
OL,17,Falso provide us with the opportunity
OL,18,Fto share with them the work that is
OL,19,Funderway to improve the services and
OL,20,Fcare we provide."
