OL,7,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"The number of prevention of future
OL,9,Fdeaths reports received by Betsi
OL,10,FCadwaladr University Health Board is
OL,11,Fof significant concern. This is an
OL,12,Farea of real concern that the health
OL,13,Fboard must address at pace.
OL,15,F"It has been made clear to the health
OL,16,Fboard that it needs to put in place
OL,17,Fsystems and process that ensures that
OL,18,Fit understands the root causes of the
OL,19,Fpoints raised by the coroners and that
OL,20,Fis able to address the systemic issues
OL,21,Fthat are apparent in the reports.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
